{"tid":2289452,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國大選｜ 白宮貿易顧問稱多州結果異常 若確認屬實特朗普「很可能」贏","createTime":"2020-11-17T09:11:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T09:52:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"429162ebfd29f8b35069966662e632ce57622b15","tid":2289452,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T09:11:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201117/QS5RLMDDKVADVAWZNFWKZU5IPA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201117%2FQS5RLMDDKVADVAWZNFWKZU5IPA%2F&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM40cGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=a93bf556\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201117%2FQS5RLMDDKVADVAWZNFWKZU5IPA%2F&h=768b48b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201117/QS5RLMDDKVADVAWZNFWKZU5IPA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美國大選｜<br />\n白宮貿易顧問稱多州結果異常 若確認屬實特朗普「很可能」贏<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uHA9PKTZJJIvZwQvogrGTAOTcfQ=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SXPK6HGZJFEUPDBMBJUKYEBETQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuHA9PKTZJJIvZwQvogrGTAOTcfQ%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSXPK6HGZJFEUPDBMBJUKYEBETQ.jpg&h=ccd083ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n納瓦羅稱若多州確認選舉結果有異常，特朗普很可能勝出。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普及其團隊挑戰多個州分的大選結果，白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅（Peter Navarro）表示，一旦確認這些州分的選舉「異常」，特朗普很有可能會勝出。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美國大選｜拜登籲與民主國家組聯合陣線抗中 不行「懲罰性」貿易政策<br />\n<br />\n...............................，納瓦羅接受傳媒Newsmax訪問時表示：「你只會看到一大堆奇怪的事情，我認為應該讓美國人停一停。我們希望得到可證實可驗證的選舉，這是我們真正想追求的東西。」<br />\n<br />\n納瓦羅進一步表示：「如果你考慮到所有選舉異常的情況，特朗普很有可能會贏，但是這些主流傳媒試圖告訴我們，不要為挑戰結果而糾纏，即使有各種很明顯的異常情況。」他補充指Dominion點票系統的問題特別令人關注。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美國大選｜特朗普預告「重大訴訟」 盤點關鍵州分官司進度<br />\n<br />\n內華達州克拉克縣（Clark County）的縣選舉委員會周一宣佈，未能確定縣代表的選舉結果，因為發現有大量「選票出入」。此消息傳出後特朗普立即在Twitter發文道：「內華達州取得重大勝利......克拉克縣官員對自己的選舉安全沒有信心，重大影響！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NaPeBCMqGi9WSfFnnX5NrkINGvw=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F4XAGIDRNZCE7A2NEL2Z2LWFNQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNaPeBCMqGi9WSfFnnX5NrkINGvw%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FF4XAGIDRNZCE7A2NEL2Z2LWFNQ.jpg&h=b4a85b5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特朗普表示克拉克縣不確認選舉結果影響重大。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n另外，白宮國家安全顧問奧布萊恩（Robert O&rsquo;Brien）周一在全球安全論壇表示：「如果確定由拜登及賀錦麗勝出，而現在看來將會如此，我們會有一個由美國國家安全委員會（National Security Council）領導的專業過渡程序。」<br />\n<br />\n路透社/Newsmax/美國《紐約郵報》"},{"pid":"e9f0afcfeaf5309cec3f29c79100c9a7cd36a678","tid":2289452,"uid":290314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T09:43:44.000Z","msg":"幫轉貼<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jackposobiec/status/1328561979448045574?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjackposobiec%2Fstatus%2F1328561979448045574%3Fs%3D21&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM40cGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=f43da010\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjackposobiec%2Fstatus%2F1328561979448045574%3Fs%3D21&h=9428e1b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/jackposobiec/status/1328561979448045574?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"debf9987847c5929105400f8e4abc9fad313b8a9","tid":2289452,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T09:47:43.000Z","msg":"屌 聽左好多日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50cb0abf881640dc54f3ac33bc08eaf055cc2531","tid":2289452,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T09:52:36.000Z","msg":"異常就睇到<br />\n例如得個幾%點到而家仲未點完<br />\n點點下突然停止點票<br />\n唔知係咪想拖到12月玩權變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過左12月8拜登做到總統機會係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}